# WorldCinema Interface Engine

An ultra-elegant, high-fidelity film discovery interface engineered for global curation streaming indices. Built using clean atomic components, premium typography, and explicit 4K UHD distribution targets.

## Features

- **Native Language Preservations**: Explicit tracking variables showing native title notation string headers (`original_title`).
- **Targeted Streaming Maps**: Fully functional downstream link routing protocols resolving straight to legitimate high-definition video paths.
- **Minimalist UX Frame**: Responsive structural grid layout built around asset density metrics and fluid media queries.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React (Vite Engine)
- **Styles**: Tailwind CSS
- **Icon Matrices**: Lucide React Core

